    - "Red Hat Ansible Engine 2.7 RPMs for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 Server x86_64"
    - "Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 Server - Extras RPMs x86_64"
    - "Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 Server Kickstart x86_64 7Server"
